    "601174087": {
      "metadata": {
        "title": "DOWN: The Casual Dating App",
        "subtitle": "Seeking a Meetup or Wild Date?",
        "promotional_text": null,
        "description": "Your search is over: this is where curiosity and honesty meet to create magical dates! 17+ million open-minded singles exploring and keeping it real.\n\nNo matter what kind of relationship you're seeking, you're in control\u2014express openly whether you're looking for something SERIOUS or CASUAL.\nDOWN is the most honest dating app for open-minded singles to connect, express themselves freely, and find what they truly want.\n\nDiscover your dating life in a safe space.\nYour privacy and safety are our top priorities. We employ robust measures, including photo verification, to proactively identify and mitigate inauthentic accounts and scammers\u2014creating a safe environment for you to match and chat with nearby singles. To enhance safety and provide a more authentic experience, all users must now be photo-verified. We\u2019re committed to combating inauthentic accounts to improve your experience, and we verify all users from the start.\n\nDOWN is the perfect app for singles seeking casual relationships, long-term commitments, or anything in between.\nFind attractive singles near you. Flirt, meet, date, and have fun every day!\nJoin our community of over 17 million users, be straightforward and date the honest way: If you're seeking casual fun, say \"GET DOWN.\" If you're looking for something more serious, say \"GET DATE.\" It's that simple\u2014you choose!\n\nHow DOWN Works:\nSign up once with a Mobile Number, Apple ID, or Facebook to verify your identity (don't worry\u2014we NEVER post to your Facebook wall!).\nLike singles nearby: We will only inform them if they\u2019re interested in you too!\nWhen we confirm you\u2019re both interested in chatting or ready to date, we\u2019ll notify you so you can meet!\nThe app is free to download and use. We also offer an optional subscription package called DOWN Private Membership.\n\nSubscribe to access DOWN's premium features and enjoy all the advantages\u2014giving you the best chances of success.\nPayment will be charged to your iTunes Account upon purchase.\nIf you choose the subscription option, it will automatically renew unless auto-renew is disabled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.\nYour account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours before the end of the current period, which will outline the renewal cost.\nSubscriptions can be managed by the user, and auto-renewal can be turned off through the user's Account Settings after purchase.\nNo cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period.\nAll personal data is handled in accordance with DOWN's privacy policy. More details can be found here: https://www.downapp.com/privacy.\n\nTerms and Conditions can be found here: https://www.downapp.com/terms.",
